    <Content contentid="1097" contenttypeid="STAFF" desc="Staff">
      <Description><![CDATA[ <p>
 Guests of Villa Voyage are looked after with flair by a dedicated team of professionals drawn from the local community, under the direction of the villa manager. They are trained to anticipate guests&rsquo; every whim with typical Balinese charm and a ready smile, and are very much part of the villa experience.</p>]]></Description>
      <SubContents>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[Villa Manager&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[<p> Sura is responsible for the effective day-to-day running of Villa Voyage. Fluent in English, he introduces guests to the villa on arrival and is at the end of a phone for special requests.</p>   ]]></Description>
          <Images />
        </SubContent>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[Chef]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[<p> Villa Voyage's Chef is well versed in resort and villa cuisine. Most of his recipes come from the owners’ vast travels and love of food. He puts together cool picnics, is a dab hand at dinner parties and is happy to discuss special menus and accommodate dietary requests.</p> ]]></Description>
          <Images />
        </SubContent>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[Butlers]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[<p> A butler and two housekeepers take care of cleaning and tidying the villa in shifts from 7am to 11pm. They also assist in the kitchen, and serve as waiters for indoor and alfresco dining.</p>  ]]></Description>
          <Images />
        </SubContent>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[Gardener/pool attendant]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[<p> The garden and pool at Villa Voyage is well tended by a team of gardeners.</p> ]]></Description>
          <Images />
        </SubContent>
        <SubContent>
          <Heading><![CDATA[Spa/massage]]></Heading>
          <Description><![CDATA[<p> Villa Voyage has a special arrangement with local fully trained therapists who can visit the villa to provide a range of treatments (prices on request).</p> ]]></Description>
          <Images />
